Thumbs.db

# TypeScript incremental build info
*.tsbuildinfo

# Editor / IDE
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
*.swo

# Docs & misc
docs
README.md
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md

# Ignored files directory
ignore
